About Perrigo

Perrigo Company plc is a leading global healthcare company that develops, manufactures and distributes over-the-counter (OTC) consumer goods, prescription (Rx) pharmaceuticals, nutritional products, and active pharmaceutical ingredients (API). The company is the world's largest manufacturer of OTC pharmaceutical products for the Private Label market and an industry leader in pharmaceutical technologies.


From its beginnings in 1887 as a packager of generic home remedies, Perrigo, headquartered in Ireland, has grown to become the world's largest manufacturer of OTC pharmaceutical products for the Private Label market and an industry leader in pharmaceutical technologies. Perrigo provides "Quality Affordable Healthcare Products®" across a wide variety of product categories and geographies primarily in North America, Europe, and Australia, as well as other key markets including Israel and China.
        


